g.text: Sequence diagram - 2004 (Upload a text file with the requirements of a candidate for its validation)
Request to upload a text file with the requirements of a candidate
ensures the user has operator role
Retrieves list of all candidates and asks to choose one
Retrieves list of all applications of the chosen candidate and asks to choose one
Asks to enter the path of the file
Enters the path of the file
ensures the user has operator role
saves the application file in the database
